the square is a 2017 swedish satirical drama film directed by ruben östlund and starring &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; bang , elisabeth moss , dominic west , and terry &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the film is about publicity surrounding an art installation , and was partly inspired by an installation östlund and producer &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; boman had made . it was shot in &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , stockholm and berlin . the film was entered into the 2017 cannes film festival , where it received positive reviews and won the palme d'or . it was subsequently selected for the 2017 toronto international film festival .